WEBVTT

00:00:06.920 --> 00:00:08.520
[Zakaj ne jemo žuželk?]

00:00:09.416 --> 00:00:12.124
Ljudje so stoletja uživali žuželke,

00:00:12.298 --> 00:00:13.573
od hroščev,

00:00:13.607 --> 00:00:15.421
do gosenic, kobilic,

00:00:15.455 --> 00:00:18.304
termitov in kačjih pastirjev.

00:00:18.608 --> 00:00:20.323
Navada ima celo ime:

00:00:20.323 --> 00:00:21.488
entomofagija.

00:00:21.602 --> 00:00:24.257
Zgodnji lovci nabiralci so se
verjetno učili od živali,

00:00:24.281 --> 00:00:27.370
ki so nabirale žužke, bogate z
beljakovinami in jih posnemali.

00:00:28.457 --> 00:00:31.717
Ko so z evolucijo žužki postali del
naše prehrambne tradicije,